ons tab in your\nrepository.\n\nName| Description  \n---|---  \n\ud83d\ude80 Quick Task| Instruct the agent to do something for you in your own words  \n\ud83e\udd16 Answer Question| Ask a question about your project / code  \n\ud83e\uddd9\u2642\ufe0f Generate Automation| Generate custom automations tailored to your project  \n\ud83e\uddd9\u2642\ufe0f Generate Tool| Generate custom tools tailored to your project  \n\ud83d\udd04 Import Workflow| One-click solution for adding Smart Workflows to your\nproject  \n\ud83d\udee0 Quick Code Change| Facilitate quick code modifications through an AI agent\nbased on user inputs  \n  \n### Contributing\n\nIf you'd like to contribute workflows, simply:\n\n  1. Fork the project\n  2. Run the \ud83e\uddd9\u2642\ufe0f Generate Automation or \ud83e\uddd9\u2642\ufe0f Generate Tool workflows\n  3. Customize the code the agent generated for you in a PR and merge it\n  4. Open a PR to this project\n\n## About\n\nAn open source collection of agentic Github workflows\n\nwww.pr-pilot.ai\n\n### Topics\n\nagent automation ai actions artificial-intelligence workflows github-actions\nllm\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nGPL-3.0 license\n\nActivity\n\nCustom properties\n\n### Stars\n\n1 star\n\n### Watchers\n\n1 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Contributors 2\n\n  * mlamina Marco Lamina\n  * pr-pilot-ai[bot]\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
